sparql: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?department WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Karen.Brant%40company.org> ns1:memberOf ?department . }
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?telephone WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Baldwin.Dirksen%40company.org> ns1:phone ?telephone . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?managerName WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Heinrich.Hoch%40company.org> ns1:hasManager ?manager . ?manager ns1:name ?managerName . }
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?email WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Sabrina.Geiger%40company.org> ns1:email ?email . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?employee ?name (COUNT(?product) AS ?sensorProducts) WHERE { ?employee ns1:areaOfExpertise <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Sensor> ; ns1:name ?name ; ns1:hasProductManager ?product . ?product ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Sensor> . } GROUP BY ?employee ?name ORDER BY DESC(?sensorProducts) LIMIT 1
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?employee WHERE { ?employee ns1:memberOf <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/dept-41622> . }
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?label WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/dept-41622> rdfs:label ?label . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT (COUNT(?product) AS ?count) WHERE { ?product ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Switch> ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Sensor> . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?name WHERE { ?person ns1:memberOf <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/dept-85880> ; ns1:areaOfExpertise <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Network> . ?person ns1:name ?name . }

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?department WHERE { ?employee :areaOfExpertise <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Transducer> . ?employee :memberOf ?department . }
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier WHERE { ?hardware ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Compensator> ; ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?supplier) AS ?count) WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:country dbpedia:France . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier WHERE { ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?product ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Compensator> . ?supplier ns1:addressCountry 'France' . }
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:addressLocality 'Toulouse' . }
PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:addressLocality 'Toulouse' . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?oscillator ?price WHERE { ?oscillator a ns1:Hardware ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Oscillator> ; ns1:price ?priceResource . ?priceResource ns1:amount ?price . } ORDER BY ASC(?price) LIMIT 1
PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?service ?price WHERE { ?service a :Service ; :price ?price . } ORDER BY DESC(?price) LIMIT 1

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?service ?price ?person WHERE { ?service a :Service ; :price ?priceSpec . ?priceSpec a :Price ; :amount ?price . ?service :hasProductManager ?person . } ORDER BY DESC(?price) LIMIT 1

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?coil ?width ?height WHERE { ?coil a ns1:Hardware ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Coil> ; ns1:width_mm ?width ; ns1:height_mm ?height }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?compatibleProduct ?label ?id WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-U990-5234138> ns1:compatibleProduct ?compatibleProduct . ?compatibleProduct rdfs:label ?label . ?compatibleProduct ns1:id ?id . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?product WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-U990-5234138> ns1:compatibleProduct ?product . ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?supplier ns1:country <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States> . FILTER(?product = <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-A360-3041803>) }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?potentiometer ?volume WHERE { ?potentiometer a ns1:Hardware ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Potentiometer> ; ns1:depth_mm ?depth ; ns1:height_mm ?height ; ns1:width_mm ?width . BIND(?depth * ?height * ?width AS ?volume) } ORDER BY ASC(?volume) LIMIT 1

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?coil ?weight ?depth ?height ?width WHERE { ?coil a ns1:Hardware ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Coil> ; ns1:weight_g ?weight ; ns1:depth_mm ?depth ; ns1:height_mm ?height ; ns1:width_mm ?width . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?city WHERE { ?product ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-LCD> . ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?supplier ns1:country <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States> . ?supplier ns1:addressLocality ?city . }

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?item ?price ?supplier ?supplierName ?country WHERE { ?item a :Hardware ; :price ?price ; :hasSupplier ?supplier . ?supplier :name ?supplierName ; :country ?country . } ORDER BY DESC(?price) OFFSET 5 LIMIT 5

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?supplier (ROUND(AVG(?amount) * 100) / 100 AS ?averagePrice) WHERE { ?product :hasSupplier ?supplier . ?product :price ?price . ?price :currency 'EUR' . ?price :amount ?amount . } GROUP BY ?supplier ORDER BY ?supplier

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?department WHERE { ?department a :Department . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?employee a :Employee ; :memberOf ?department ; :hasManager ?manager } }

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplierName ?addressCountry ?addressLocality ?addressText ?addressCountryCode WHERE { ?supplier a :Supplier . OPTIONAL { ?supplier :addressCountry ?addressCountry } . OPTIONAL { ?supplier :addressLocality ?addressLocality } . OPTIONAL { ?supplier :addressText ?addressText } . OPTIONAL { ?supplier :addressCountryCode ?addressCountryCode } . OPTIONAL { ?supplier :name ?supplierName } }

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?agent ?category WHERE { ?agent :areaOfExpertise ?category . VALUES ?category { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Compensator> <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Crystal> <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-LCD> }

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?item ?width ?height ?depth WHERE { ?item a :Hardware ; :width_mm ?width ; :height_mm ?height ; :depth_mm ?depth . FILTER(?width > ?height && ?depth < 50) }

PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?productA ?productB WHERE { ?productA prod:compatibleProduct ?productB . ?productB prod:compatibleProduct ?productA . FILTER(?productA != ?productB) }
PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?item ?id ?name ?width WHERE { ?item a :Hardware ; :width_mm ?width ; :id ?id ; :name ?name . } ORDER BY DESC(?width) LIMIT 100

PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?supplier ?index WHERE { ?inductor :hasCategory :prod-cat-Inductor ; :reliabilityIndex ?index ; :hasSupplier ?supplier . } ORDER BY DESC(?index) LIMIT 1

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX ns2: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?country WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/bom-17> ns1:hasBomPart ?bomPart . ?bomPart ns1:hasPart ?hardwarePart . ?hardwarePart ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?supplier ns1:addressCountry ?country . }
PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?bom WHERE { ?bom :hasBomPart ?part . ?part :hasSupplier ?supplier . }

PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?supplier) AS ?numSuppliers) WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-K367-1320550> ns1:compatibleProduct ?compatibleProduct . ?compatibleProduct ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . }
